::Ramulus/Striker/Ramhorn/Smokescreen::

Ramulus jumps backwards, the impact of Sixshot's crash, even if the bot hit 
in front of him, flipping Ramulus backwards.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker jumps backwards from Hades, his arm mutilated and bleeding. He pulls 
out a pistol, firing it at Hades.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramhorn throws his last charge at Shuko, jumping from behind his boulder and 
firing at Serpentor along with Smokescreen.
